direction: right
A: "Sensor readings"
B: "MQTT broker" { shape: queue }
C: "Pipeline consumer"
D: "TimescaleDB (hot)" { shape: cylinder }
E: "Parquet / MinIO (cold)" { shape: cylinder }
Q: "Data-quality monitor\n(rolling variance)"
F: "Features: rolling CO2, rate,\noccupancy, time-of-day"
G: "Autonomous service"
H: "Overnight occupancy study"
